story.text: Jimmy is here and finding all sorts of ammonites and other fossils. Sooooo cool. Still sick. Sad face. Need to get to sleep earlier today. I love these two. I hope they decide to buy a place in the valley before it gets stupid expensive.
Also, headache but I don't care.
